name: Gigi Hadid
description:
Gigi Hadid

Supermodel

Continuing testing my LoRA prowess, here is world famous model Gigi Hadid. I know next to nothing about her other than she may be related to the last LoRA I did.

I used 30 high-definition images, 75 steps each, kohya_ss defaults otherwise.

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!

She looks best 0.4-0.6, gradients included in my examples below.
